    <h1>YouTube Shorts</h1>
    <p class="description">Vertical videos up to <strong>3 minutes long</strong> surfaced in YouTube's dedicated swipe-feed. Separate algorithm from long-form, own monetisation pool, and one of the fastest paths to reaching new audiences on YouTube in 2026.</p>
