            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>The ideal Short length depends on content type. High-retention 15-30 second Shorts perform well in the swipe feed. Tutorial and how-to content tends to perform better at 45-90 seconds. Shorts longer than 90 seconds need a very strong hook to avoid swipes.</p></div></div>
          </div>
